OL,3,CCase of man accused of murdering 17-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl adjourned for legal
OL,5,Creasons
OL,7,FThe case of a man accused of murdering
OL,8,Fa 17-year-old in Blaenau Gwent and the
OL,9,Fattempted murder of her mother has
OL,10,Fbeen adjourned for legal reasons.
OL,12,FAn inquest heard Lainie Williams died
OL,13,Fof stab wounds at her home in Cefn
OL,14,FForest near Blackwood last November.
OL,16,FHer mother, Rhian Stephens, received
OL,17,Fhospital treatment for her injuries.
OL,19,FCameron Cheng, 19, is accused of
OL,20,Fmurder, attempted murder, and
OL,21,Fpossession of a bladed article.
