OL,3,CCase of man accused of murdering 17-
OL,4,Cyear-old girl adjourned for legal
OL,5,Creasons
OL,7,FGwent Police officers, including
OL,8,Ffirearms personnel, attended the
OL,9,Fproperty on Wheatley Place at around
OL,10,F7:15am on 13 November 2025 after
OL,11,Freceiving reports that two people had
OL,12,Fsuffered serious injuries.
OL,14,FTributes have been paid to Lainie
OL,15,Fsince her death, including a GoFundMe
OL,16,Fpage, set up by Lainie's cousin Shania
OL,17,FPrice.
